<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Peter, uns sind seid des <app>
<note><q type="date"><expan>nehstv<ex>er</ex>gang<ex>en</ex></expan> montags
                        </q>15.09.1421</note> <expan>ab<ex>end</ex></expan>
</app> drey deinr brief <expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan>, der
                                <expan>datu<ex>m</ex></expan> heltt <app>
<note><q type="date">am <expan>nehstv<ex>er</ex>gang<ex>en</ex></expan>
                                    samstag</q>13.09.1421</note>
</app>, <app>
<note><q type="date">sunntag</q>14.09.1421</note>
</app> und <app>
<note><q type="date">montag nach
                                <expan>cruc<ex>is</ex></expan></q>15.09.1421</note>
</app>, daran wir die lewff <expan>eygenlich<ex>er</ex></expan> denn vor
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> und des ein
                                <expan>wolfgefalle<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>. So <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir, du
                        habst <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> brief auch wol
                            <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>, <expan>besund<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir dir <app>
<note><q type="date"><expan>am<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>nehst<ex>en</ex></expan> montag</q>15.09.1421</note>
</app>
<expan>geschribe<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz wir dir vor vi halpvass weins, iiii
                                <expan>frank<ex>en</ex></expan> und ii
                            <expan>ellsess<ex>er</ex></expan> gen <expan>Eg<ex>er</ex></expan> zum
                        Niclas <expan>Gum<ex>m</ex>eraw<ex>er</ex></expan> gesandt
                                <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, was du im
                            <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> schreibst <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        empewtst, daz er das tun sülle. Also <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir nu
                                <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> kawft zwen weͣgen weins nemlich v vass,
                        der sind iɉ <expan>gut<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ellsess<ex>er</ex></expan>, die iii <expan>frank<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>gemein<ex>er</ex></expan> speiswein, die wir dir auch
                                <expan>unv<ex>er</ex>czogenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gen Eger zum Niclas
                                <expan>Gum<ex>m</ex>eraw<ex>er</ex></expan> schiken und befelhen
                        wellen, was du im <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> schreibst oder empewtst,
                        daz er das auch tun sol, da wiss dich nach zu
                            <expan>richte<ex>n</ex></expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>s<ex>ub</ex></expan> sigillo
                            <expan>m<ex>a</ex>g<ex>ist</ex>ri</expan>
<expan>civiu<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>sab<ex>at</ex>o</expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
